HEADWORD: Longboat
<hw>Long"boat`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Naut.)</fld>
<def>Formerly, the largest boat carried by a merchant vessel,
corresponding to the launch of a naval vessel.</def>⟦br⟧
